"Late" was an obscure single released in very limited numbers by the band &lt;a href="Blue%20Angel%20%28band%29"&gt;Blue Angel&lt;/a&gt;, taken from their 1980 album also called "&lt;a href="Blue%20Angel%20%28Blue%20Angel%20album%29"&gt;Blue Angel&lt;/a&gt;". Lee Brovitz was the primary songwriter, sharing co-writing credits with Lauper and Turi.
